dct_description_sm: New Jersey. Department of Conservation and Development. Division of Geology and Topography. Atlas Sheet 35 (1930) New Jersey Geological Survey. Relief show by 10 and 5 ft. contour interval and spot heights. Depth shown by contour ans soundiings in feet at low tide.Title was not given. Region covered: vicinity of Millville. Original survey 1886, principal culture revised 1917, 1929. Original survey and revisions to 1917 made under direction of C. C. Vermeule, Topographer. Revision of 1929 by L. P. Plummer, Topographic Engineer.
dct_publisher_sm: Trenton, N.J. : New Jersey Geological Survey, 1930.
